-- Morgan Stanely's Siniscalco Expects Italian M&A Recovery to Lag Europe's
-- B y   E l i s a   M a r t i n u z z i
-- 2010-10-05T08:34:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/morgan-stanely-s-siniscalco-expects-italian-m-a-recovery-to-lag-europe-s.html
Former Finance Minister Domenico
Siniscalco said the recovery in Italian mergers and acquisitions
will lag Europe by a year, speaking at a conference in Milan.  Italian mergers and acquisitions are “like a severely
half-empty glass,” Siniscalco, who is head of Morgan Stanley’s
Italian business, said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisa Martinuzzi in Milan at 
 emartinuzzi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
